title: Jack Du Brul - The Philip Mercer Series
description:
Here are the seven novels of the Philip Mercer series by Jack Du Brul, co-author of the last seven of Clive Cussler's Oregon Files series.
If you enjoyed those, you may well enjoy these. ?

All books are in both .mobi and.epub formats.
